alysis on every render**\n`src/frontend/LinearCanvas.js:23-89` ‚Äî `ToneHUD` recalculates tone metrics on every render regardless of whether `blockText` changed.\n```js\nconst toneMetrics = useMemo(() => analyzeBlockTone(blockText), [blockText]);\n```\n\n**SimplifiiStudio.js: `sectionHealth` recomputed in render loop**\n`src/frontend/SimplifiiStudio.js:152-169` ‚Äî health metrics recalculated for each section on every render.\n```js\nconst health = useMemo(() => sectionHealth(sectionText), [sectionText]);\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Caching Opportunities\n\n**BriefService.js: Regex compiled inside function body**\n`src/services/BriefService.js:127-163` ‚Äî patterns like `/\\bhow\\s+to\\b/gi` compiled fresh on every call to `extractDeepCourseData`.\n```js\n// Module level ‚Äî compiled once\nconst PATTERN_HOW_TO = /\\bhow\\s+to\\b/gi;\nconst PATTERN_STEPS   = /\\bsteps\\b/gi;\n```\n\n**MessagingHub.js: Voice search repeated each utterance**\n`src/services/MessagingHub.js:104-118` ‚Äî `__pickVoice` scans the full voices array on every synthesis call.\n```js\nlet __cachedVoice = null;\nconst __pickVoice = (name, lang) => {\n  if (__cachedVoice?.name === name) return __cachedVoice;\n  __cachedVoice = /* search */;\n  return __cachedVoice;\n};\n```\n\n**RewriteService.js: Synonym lookups without a cache**\nSynonym resolution for the same `(term, level)` pair repeats on every rewrite; a `Map` keyed on `term:level` eliminates the redundancy.\n\n---\n\n### 4. Redundant Computations\n\n**LiteralMode.js: Sequential regex chain**\n`src/core/LiteralMode.js:22-91` ‚Äî `literalise` applies patterns one-by-one via `reduce`. Where patterns are non-overlapping, combine into a single alternation regex with a lookup table to do one pass.\n\n**BriefService.js: Multiple regex passes on same string**\n`src/services/BriefService.js:215-253` ‚Äî assessment title parser runs several `.match`/`.test` calls on the same string. Collapse into one regex with named capture groups.\n```js\nconst match = 